to excite the conservative instincts most of us have 
most of the protest has appeared in the letters columns of the 
times 
a h atkins wrote in to argue that the existing lyrics 
represent an outspoken and truly british sentiment 
noel brandonjones asked the commission to explain how god is 
to save the queen without frustrating the knavish tricks of her 
enemies both at home and abroad 
