this tranquil himalayan kingdoms capital 
is becoming a sea of violence and hatred and the latest target is 
the police force widely despised for its longtime repression of 
prodemocracy activits 
until a few months ago nepal was known more for its mountains 
tourist resorts and trekking trails than for riots curfews and 
