these drug traffickers are doing and are not making a big profit 
off of it youre putting us on rangel said 
the bill is aimed at addressing the 110 billion in us cash 
drug transactions that the treasury department estimates are 
laundered through the world financial system every year despite 
laws to thwart it 
we put the street dealer in jail and we put the drug kingpin 
