aerial attack on the voracious insects 
the infestation covers some 700000 acres in five counties of 
northcentral nevada with crickets counted at up to 100 per square 
foot in some areas near winnemucca 160 miles northeast of reno 
i think weve made real progress in killing the insects 
although theres a lot of them out there said dick rowe 
