as they seek to shape the alliance from a military organization to 
a more political one 
an announcement of moves to end the nuclear missile project and 
trim battlefield nuclear artillery could come at an expected 
summit possibly in the summer of the leaders of the 16 nato 
nations the sources said speaking on condition of anonymity 
