allegedly fishing inside us waters northwest of the pribilof 
islands in the bering sea the coast guard said 
the yocona was dispatched to intercept the trawler and thursday 
morning ordered the soviet ship to halt but the vessel attempted 
to elude the cutter and return to international waters 
