escalation of words and more attention focused on michael mcgee 
than on the issues 
murtaugh said mcgee wants only to rectify the violence of 
racism that has isolated blacks within an 8 by 5mile block on 
the citys north side that is plagued by crime poverty unsafe 
housing and unemployment 
