whats this john waters the impresario of 
bad taste hooked up with the people who gave you parenthood 
whats more his new film cry baby is being released by a 
mainstream company universal pictures has the onetime king of 
underground sleaze succumbed to the establishment 
ive always tried to make commercial movies he explains 
unapologetically think about it pink flamingos 1972 cost 
10000 all the hideousness i put in that movie was commercial 
nobody heard of us before all the people who left that movie said 
oh my god you wouldnt believe what i just saw 
i always try to be commercial on my terms it worked too 
that movies still playing two generations have been offended by 
that movie im proud of that its hard to do 
talk about inflation cry baby cost 8 million minor by 
hollywood standards but not waters the film is backed by 
universal and imagine films entertainment operated by ron howard 
and brian grazer makers of splash and parenthood 
they have been a wonderful support said waters they 
never said to me you cant do that they gave me the money to do 
everything i wanted to do hire all the stars in heaven 
well not quite cry baby stars johnny depp the teen rage 
of tvs 21 jump street and amy locane as starcrossed lovers 
in the 1950s the cast ranges from polly bergen and susan tyrell to 
traci lords and iggy pop with cameos by willem dafoe patty hearst 
david ozzie and harriet nelson and troy donahue its all set 
to the beat of early rock n roll 
i wanted it to look like a 50s musical like the girl cant 
help it or early elvis waters said or like the spinoff 
lower versions of the wild one or rebel without a cause i 
liked those movies but better i liked the cheap imitations 
a movie nut all his life waters confessed his lifelong 
