picture 
although waters films are treasured at saturday midnight 
screenings he insists that he enjoys a wide audience after 
hairspray had been out we found that 8 and 9yearolds really 
loved the films thats an audience i had never tested never even 
thought of they liked it on one level they didnt see the parody 
of it 
when we tested cry baby there were a lot of kids who said 
they thought it was a really romantic movie they can like it on a 
another level thats ok it is romantic it is sexy all juvenile 
delinquents were sexy thats why they had em the word itself is 
sexy we dont have juvenile delinquents anymore we have 
13yearold mass murderers 
